上訴審裁判費。\r\n中　　華　　民　　國　　110 　年　　11　　月　　26　　日\r\n                              書記官　廖文瑜","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/LTEV/110%2c%e7%be%85%e7%b0%a1%2c194%2c20211126%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"LTEV,110,羅簡,194,20211126,1","JYEAR":"110","JCASE":"羅簡","JNO":"194","JDATE":"20211126","JTITLE":"清償債務"}